{"tid":1335602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.21前夕，入嚟聽下天琦想同大家講啲咩","createTime":"2019-07-20T14:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T15:27:01.000Z","uid":59297,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad366f60b727678e6e393d379fce29d0c52227a","tid":1335602,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要聽晒佢！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVEUhAVki0DA&d=5riwYeXkLlljSywqzybc4m9V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=d0b6095a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然係三年前嘅演講，但天琦講嘅野都係好值得我地反思。<br />\n7.21大戰前夕，希望大家聽完有個心理準備再上戰場。<br />\n要記住我地嘅夢想係咩，我地香港人點解要行出嚟！<br />\n我地香港人只有一個目標，就係贏！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「黎明之前嘅黑暗係至撚黑暗嘅，但係黎明即將會來臨。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7.21 香港人企出嚟！<br />\n光復香港！！！<br />\n時代革命！！！<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"261676730a89801978fb979bf8ea333276f9dd54","tid":1335602,"uid":238051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:54:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保障同行手足<br />\n向偽警說不！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【7.21有人冒警】和理非對偽警說不！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335553</a>"},{"pid":"b1077171a38cb66f72cb3e2561e7280dd04e7b81","tid":1335602,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"fd05dd28ad9a887cfe9a1a0bb62f8ecc11c4b92e","tid":1335602,"uid":59297,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:58:34.000Z","msg":"「我冇辦法走入呢座立法會大樓，但唔緊要，依家然有第二個人會取代我，後繼絕對一